Text: FW Enhancing Leadership PPHeres what I had prepared earlier Good to talk with you today Give me a call when you have a chance to review this Thanks Joe Original Message From mailto Sent Thursday June PM To Cc Subject Enhancing Leadership PP To Rick Shapiro Enron From Joe Synan Date June Re Enhancing the Leadership Rick I have prepared the attached as possibly helpful to enhancing the leadership I am sorry this was so long in coming I dropped the ball on this before I took vacation then discovered my error when I returned Ill call to follow up Thanks Enron State Gov PPdoc
